cd …

item.dc:creator: @iKilem iKilem
item.description:
@iKilem wrote:

There aren’t any compiling errors, but you do have a note saying you’re using a deprecated API.

It’s possible that your current JRE isn’t recognising the code. Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation, e.g.

javac *.java -Xlint:deprecation

'And then post the output.
